programme.title: McMillan
programme.desc: Part 1. Auction winner Bryan DeWitt joins Tom McMillan and Clint Bowyer on a one-of-a-kind, not-to-be-repeated hog hunt that goes from zero to 100 in a split second(n)

programme.title: Sweetwater
programme.desc: Miles and Joey team up with Anthony Randazzo of Paradise Plus fishing lodge to go hunt bull red fish in Venice, La. The fertile waters of the Mississippi River meet the Gulf of Mexico and creates the ideal conditions for a booming red fish population(n)

programme.title: In-Fisherman *
programme.desc: It's right up the staff's alley to cut through any complications on the way to fine fishing. They use live bait for snook; slip into two-timing mode to do battle with crappies, perch and largemouths on ice; and reveal spoon secrets for smallmouths(n)

programme.title: The Western Hunter *
programme.desc: Nate ends up on Kodiak Island on short notice to hunt Sitka blacktail deer with his friend, Wayne Endicott, after unforeseen circumstances left an open seat on Wayne's long-planned hunting trip(n)

programme.title: Pure Hunting
programme.desc: Family health issues cause Willi to back out of a father-son duck hunt with family friends, but he sends his dad on his way for a new waterfowl adventure. Also: we learn what Ducks Unlimited has done with its conservation efforts in south Texas(n)

programme.title: Fresh Tracks With Randy Newberg
programme.desc: Randy helps sweepstakes winner, Justin Hall, as they try to find a good New Mexico bull. Justin traveled from Kansas to see and hear his first elk as a result of winning Randy's sweepstakes hunt(n)

programme.title: Petersen's Hunting Adventures
programme.desc: Part 2. Craig Boddington and Steve Hornady are on a bucket list safari in Uganda. Tag along as they hunt Nile buffalo and track plains game across the long-grass savanna and fish the headwaters of the mighty Nile on this epic adventure(n)

programme.title: Long Range Pursuit
programme.sub-title: Wilderness Quest With Garrett and Kregg Part II
programme.desc: Part 2. After a successful tahr hunt, Kregg and Garrett embark on a quest to take a free-range stag(n)

programme.title: MeatEater
programme.desc: Hunting pigeons and doves in Virginia(n)

programme.title: Guns & Ammo TV *
programme.desc: Crimson Trace introduces its new Linq laser/light system for ARs and AKs. Home defense is the topic in Real World Training(n)

programme.title: GunVenture
programme.desc: Field host KJ returns to his home state for some wild, rapid running near the heart of downtown Oklahoma City. Then, a nighttime hog hunt with Trijicon. Also: a trip to Fouled Bore Precision for some long-range tips and a timely battle(n)

programme.title: Small Town Hunting
programme.desc: Kevin Meacham stays home at the office while the guys head to Texas to hunt the Harris Ranch in January for deer and again in March for gobbling Rios(n)

programme.title: Adrenaline
programme.desc: The rut is rolling throughout the Midwest as the crews are burning the whitetail candle at both ends. As one Iowa crew hit their low point, a known giant coined “Bodacious” shows himself for a close friend(n)

programme.title: Whitetail Slam
programme.desc: Dr. James Kroll takes viewers into the land of the desert Coues deer. These tiny deer are thought to be the only whitetails with a clean blood line, as their population is separated by hundreds of miles from other deer(n)

programme.title: Wildlifers *
programme.desc: The Wildlifers are back home at the Mellon Creek Ranch in Refugio, Texas, giving us a small glimpse of some of the abundant wildlife the ranch has to offer(n)

programme.title: Extreme Outer Limits TV
programme.desc: Bob and Chris Beck hunt elk in the high country of Wyoming at Star Valley Outfitters(n)

programme.title: Big Boys TV
programme.desc: Part 2. Kevin continues to guide his elk hunters in Michigan while the rut is in full swing(n)

programme.title: The Most Wanted List
programme.desc: The hunt in Idaho continues, but the game has changed. It's a family affair as Kristy's brother, Sonny, and guest, Josie, hunt elk and whitetail(n)

programme.title: Winchester Deadly Passion
programme.desc: The Nebraska Sandhills have become a favorite destination for Melissa Bachman when it comes to big mule deer. After a tough archery hunt earlier in the season, Bachman returns to do a self-filmed hunt that ends with a pretty incredible buck up close(n)
